Package shared.model

Class Transmission

java.lang.Object
shared.model.Transmission
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class Transmission
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
Represents a single transmission from client-to-server, or from server-to-client. Each transmission has an action, and contains the associated object(s) used for the transmission.
Since:
13-03-2020
Version:
1.0
Author:
Parker Link
